### Import summary

Just trying to trick your script!  :smile:

I have no idea why the build failed on the latest commit. The error is:
> curl: (3) URL using bad/illegal format or missing URL

But it doesn't seem like the arguments to `curl` changed in any meaningful way?

I think that the code fell into the trap that I had set: there were two matching id's, so `comment_id` was `id1\nid2` instead of `id1`.

I now made the script take the first matching id, hoping that since the bot posts on each pull request, its message will be the first (and likely only) beginning with `### Import summary`.

Pull request successfully merged into master.
